# Vendors

Third-party services this stack depends on. Tracked at the
orchestrator level so renewals, risks, and switch costs are
visible without spelunking through each sub-repo's `package.json`.

> Updated when: a vendor is added, a contract changes, a renewal
> approaches, or at the quarterly review.

## Format

```markdown
## {{vendor name}}

- **Used for:** {{what role it plays in the stack}}
- **Sub-repos depending on it:** {{api, ios, web, ...}}
- **Plan / tier:** {{...}}
- **Renewal:** {{YYYY-MM-DD or "month-to-month"}}
- **Contractual SLA:** {{e.g. 99.9% uptime, 4h support response}}
- **Switch cost:** {{low / medium / high — and why}}
- **Risk if outage:** {{what breaks, for whom, for how long}}
- **Account owner:** {{...}}
- **Notes:** {{...}}
```

